dataflowSinks.name: UserQuerywranggling
dataflowSinks.script:
sink(allowSchemaDrift: true,
	validateSchema: false,
	input(
		OrderID as string,
		OrderDate as string,
		CustomerName as string,
		ProductName as string,
		Quantity as string,
		PriceEach as string,
		Total as string,
		Country as string,
		Status as string
	),
	umask: 0022,
	preCommands: [],
	postCommands: [],
	skipDuplicateMapInputs: true,
	skipDuplicateMapOutputs: true) ~> UserQuerywranggling
